              <p>Promote a clicular conomy and eco-friendly practices</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="fea-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-hands-holding-circle"></i></div>
              <h3>Planet-Positive Choices</h3>
              <p>Connect people with planet-positive choices by curating sustainable alternatives that reduce waste and
                promote mindful consumption</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="fea-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-recycle"></i></div>
              <h3>Everyday Sustainability Made Simple</h3>
              <p>Promote & inspire eco-conscious lifestyles by making sustainable products easy to find, trust, and
                afford.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
              <div class="fea-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-dove"></i></div>
              <h3>Sustainable Shopping for All</h3>
              <p>To make sustainability the standard by offering responsibly sourced and upcycled goods to
